name: Experiment Or Die #64
description: Project to create a new collage every day for a year using my years of personal assets. One of the greatest films of all time is getting a long awaited 4th installment at the end of this year. I have high expectations but we will all have to wait and see if it's any good. And the largest generative NFT project to date is releasing tomorrow and to commemorate the release I watched The Matrix TWICE and honored it with todays design. Free Your Mind!
